sequenceDiagram
    participant C as gRPC Consumer
    participant A as AckMessageActivity
    participant M as MessagingProcessor
    participant P as AckMessageProcessor
    participant B as PopBufferMergeService
    participant R as Revive Topic / PopConsumerService
    participant V as PopReviveService

    C->>A: AckMessage
    A->>M: ackMessage / batchAckMessage
    M->>P: ACK_MESSAGE / BATCH_ACK_MESSAGE
    P->>B: 尝试合并 ACK
    alt 合并成功
        B-->>P: 完成
    else 旧版 Revive 路径
        P->>R: 写入 ACK 记录
        V->>R: 扫描 CK 与 ACK
    else KV POP 路径
        P->>R: PopConsumerService.ackAsync
    end
    P-->>C: ACK 结果
